  augroup ZenkakuSpace
    autocmd!
    autocmd ColorScheme       * call ZenkakuSpace()
    autocmd VimEnter,WinEnter * match ZenkakuSpace /ã€€/
  augroup END
  call ZenkakuSpace()
endif


